(2101, 160566, '2012-10-14 16:08:17', '"All of the tested RSBCs [regular-spiking basket cells] were positive\nfor CCK [cholecystokinin] (Fig. 3A; 21 of 21 tested cells)\nbut were negative for SOM [somatostatin] and PV [parvalbumin] (0 of\n20, 0 of 2, respectively)."', 'p 4243 right mid', 'data', NULL, NULL),
