(2245, 160692, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', '"BSCs [bistratified cells] show a fast-spiking discharge pattern. They express\nPV [parvalbumin], the neuropeptides SOM [somatostatin], NPY [neuropeptide Y], and high levels of the GABA[gamma aminobutyric acid receptor]A-alpha 1 (Pawelzik\net al., 2002; Klausberger et al., 2004; Baude et al., 2007). This type constitutes\n~25% of all PV-immunopositive cells and ~ 5% of GABAergic interneurons in the\nCA1 area (Baude et al., 2007)."', 'p 48 bot', 'data', NULL, NULL),
(2246, 160692, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', NULL, NULL, 'protocol', NULL, NULL),
(2247, 160692, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', NULL, NULL, 'animal', NULL, NULL),
(2248, 160694, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', '"Ivy cells are immunoreactive for NOS [nitric oxide synthase] and NPY [neuropeptide Y] and express high\nlevels of the alpha-1 subunit of GABA[gamma aminobutyric acid]A receptors, but are consistently negative\nfor PV [parvalbumin]."', 'p 50 top', 'data', NULL, NULL),
(2249, 160694, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', NULL, NULL, 'protocol', NULL, NULL),
(2250, 160694, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', NULL, NULL, 'animal', NULL, NULL),
(2251, 160696, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', '"The main markers [of Schaffer collateral-associated cells] are CCK [cholecystokinin] and CB [calbindin] (Cope et al., 2002; Pawelzik\net al., 2002)."', 'p 50 bot', 'data', NULL, NULL),
(2252, 160696, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', NULL, NULL, 'protocol', NULL, NULL),
(2253, 160696, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', NULL, NULL, 'animal', NULL, NULL),
(2254, 160698, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', '"Neurochemical markers of PPA [perforant path-associated] cells include\nCCK [cholecytokinin] (Pawelzik et al., 2002; Klausberger et al., 2005) and they may also express CB [calbinidin]."', 'p 51 bot', 'data', NULL, NULL),
(2255, 160698, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', NULL, NULL, 'protocol', NULL, NULL),
(2256, 160698, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', NULL, NULL, 'animal', NULL, NULL),
(2257, 160700, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', '"NG [neurogliaform] cells express NPY [neuropeptide Y] and NOS [nitric oxide synthase] (Price et al., 2005)."', 'p 52 top', 'data', NULL, NULL),
(2258, 160700, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', NULL, NULL, 'protocol', NULL, NULL),
(2259, 160700, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', NULL, NULL, 'animal', NULL, NULL),
(2260, 160702, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', '"These [oriens--lacunosum-moleculare] interneurons are immunopositive for SOM [somatostatin], the metabotropic glutamate receptor\nmGluR la, weakly positive for PV [parvalbumin], and may also contain NPY [neuropeptide Y] (Kosaka et al., 1988;\nBaude et al., 1993; Klausberger et al., 2003)."', 'p 52 mid', 'data', NULL, NULL),
(2261, 160702, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', NULL, NULL, 'protocol', NULL, NULL),
(2262, 160702, '2012-10-14 16:08:20', NULL, NULL, 'animal', NULL, NULL),
