(2719, 150120, '2012-10-14 16:08:29', '"Figure 1.  In vivo firing patterns and visualization of a CCK [cholecystokinin]-expressing basket cell (T64c).  A, Reconstruction of the soma and dendrites (orange) is shown complete; the axon (yellow) is shown only from three sections of 65 microm thickness for clarity.  st.rad., Stratum radiatum; st. pyr., stratum pyramidale; st. or., stratum oriens.  Scale bar, 100 microm.  B, Light (DAB reaction) and immuno-fluorescence microscopic visualization of the labeled cell (asterisk) demonstrates expression of CCK but not PV [parvalbumin].  Note an adjacent PV-expressing cell (arrow). Scale bar, 20 microm."', 'p 9784, Figure 1', 'data', NULL, NULL),
