(2842, 161056, '2012-10-14 16:08:31', '"Unlike PV-IR\ncells, CCK-IR basket cells express CB1 cannabinoid recep-\ntors in their axon terminals (Katona et al., 1999b) and\nsubstance P receptors in their soma/dendrites (Acsa´dy et\nal., 1997), whereas PV-IR cells express dendritic mu-opioid\nreceptors (Bausch, 1998 and references therein). The ac-\ntivity of these two types of interneurones will thus be\ndifferentially modulated."', 'p 366 left mid', 'data', NULL, NULL),
