(2976, 161134, '2012-10-14 16:08:33', '"Examination of the PV-positive inter-\nneuron population revealed no co-localization with a-\nactinin-2 (Fig. 3a, b; Table 1). Alpha-actinin-2 also\nshowed a lack of double labeling in CB-positive inter-\nneurons (Fig. 3c, d; Table 1). Additionally, neither VIP\nnor CCK co-localized with a-actinin-2 (Table 1)."', 'p341, left mid', 'data', NULL, NULL),
