(3033, 161174, '2012-10-14 16:08:34', '"The labeled bistratified cells were tested for the expression of various\nCa2+-binding  proteins, neuropeptides  and  neurotransmitter-\nreceptors using immunofluorescence microscopy (Table 1). All tested\nbistratified  cells  were  positive  for  parvalbumin, somatostatin  and\nneuropeptide Y, and their plasma membranes were strongly positive\nfor the alpha1 subunit of the GABAA receptor (Fig. 2); but no expression\nof calbindin, calretinin, metabotropic glutamate receptor 1alpha, or mus-\ncarinic  acetylcholine  receptor  type  2  could  be  detected  in  their\nsomato-dendritic domains."', 'p42, right mid', 'data', NULL, NULL),
