(4076, 406, '2012-10-14 16:07:28', 'CA1 (-)3222 perforant path-associated (PPA) neurons', 'Perforant path assoc (-)3222', 'active', 'Status: active\r\n\r\nMerger status:\r\nThis packet is a result of a merger between CA1 (-)3220 perforant path-associated (PPA) neurons and CA1 (-)3202 perforant path-associated (PPA) neurons.\r\n\r\nRejected merger between CA1 (-)3202 perforant path-associated (PPA) neurons and CA1 (-)1202 pyramidal/radiatum-lacunosum moleculare (PR-LM) neurons. \r\n\r\nCross-references:\r\nCA3 (-)30000 stratum lacunosum-moleculare (SLM) neurons (suspended)\r\nCA3 (-)23100 associational commissural-associated (ACA) neurons (suspended)\r\nCA3 (-)03000 radiatum-calbindin (R-CB) neurons (active)\r\nCA3 (-)02320 mossy fiber-associated (MFA) neurons (suspended)\r\nCA1 (-)3300p-DG 1110 perforant path I (PP I) neurons (active)\r\nCA1 (-)3300 neurgliaform--lacunosum moleculare (NGF-LM) neurons (active)\r\nCA1 (-)3220 perforant path associated (PPA) neurons (new)\r\nCA1 (-)3000 neurogliaform II (NGF II) neurons (active)\r\nCA1 (-)2333 bistratified-trilaminar neurons (active)\r\nCA1 (-)2232 basket cells (BC) (active)\r\nCA1 (-)1003 oriens--lacunosum-moleculare (O-LM) neurons (new)\r\nCA1 (-)0333 bistratified-ivy neurons (active)\r\nCA1 (-)0313 radial trilaminar neurons (suspended)\r\nCA1 (-)0311 basket cells (BC) (new)\r\nCA1 (-)0300 Schaffer collateral associated-stratum radiatum-calbindin (SCA-SR-CB) neurons (active)\r\nCA1 (-)0113p-SUB 111 trilaminar horizontal-oriens retrohippocampal projecting-double projecting-oriens (TH-ORP-DP-OR) neurons (active)\r\nCA1 (-)0113 oriens-bistratified (O-Bi) neurons (new)\r\nCA1 (-)0012 axo-axonic (AA) neurons (active)\r\nCA1 (-)0012 perisomatic-targeting interneurons (PTI) (active)\r\nCA1 (-)0003 stratum oriens-stratum oriens (SO-SO) neurons (active)\r\n\r\nRelated classes:\r\nCA1 (-)3200p-DG 1000-SUB 100 perforant path II (PP II) neurons (active)\r\n\r\nNotes:\r\nTricoire (2011): Borderline D:SLM.'),
