(6033, 627, '2012-10-14 16:07:28', 'MEC (+)001331 multipolar neurons V (MPN V)', 'Multipolar V (+)001331', 'active', 'Status: active\r\n\r\nMerger status:\r\nFailed unofficial merger proposal with 002331 globular IV/V because evidence in that packet is too weak.\r\n\r\nNotes:\r\nLikely excitatory cells (Canto & Witter 201X MEC preprint -> projecting, spiny to sparsely spiny, "principal").\r\n\r\nPacket formerly included only the Canto MEC multipolar neuron (pg 3, rightmost cell).  Packet now also includes horizontally tilted pyramidal neuron (same page, second cell from right).  Now, clearly, n > 1.'),
