(6049, 639, '2012-10-14 16:07:28', 'EC (-)023000 multipolar inhibitory 3 III (MPI 3 III) neurons', 'Multiform III (-)023000', 'active', 'Status: Approved \r\n\r\nMerger status: \r\nNo current merger proposals.\r\n\r\nFailed unofficial merger proposal with EC 023100 bipolar 2 because MPI cells project to the hippocampus and there isn''t evidence that these cells do that.\r\n   \r\nNotes:  These cells are also found in layer II\r\n\r\nAxon to hippocampus.\r\n\r\nInhibitory because of GABA immunoreactivity and sparsely spiny dendrites.'),
