(1099, 612436, '2012-10-14 16:08:00', '"Briefly, transverse hippocampal slices (300350 microm thick) were cut on a vibratome (Oxford series 1000) from SpragueDawley rats postnatal day (P) 1622 after isoflurane anesthesia."', 'p5334, right bot', 'data', NULL, NULL);
